{"tid":2126522,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"朝早一返工梗係去爆石！！！！！點知中伏","createTime":"2020-07-27T01:39:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-27T01:59:34.000Z","uid":26018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1c3aef04266248c8317a73aa15581c93eb3c540e","tid":2126522,"uid":26018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T01:39:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一大朝梗係去爆左石先做野<br />\n<br />\n點知屎眼癡住左啲紙巾<br />\n<br />\n諗住自己好醒<br />\n<br />\n肢啲消毒落紙巾抺下個屎眼<br />\n<br />\n一抺個下<br />\n<br />\n終於知咩叫屎眼著火<br />\n屌！！！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n那到：「嗚！！！！」一聲叫左出來<br />\n<br />\n隔離左右應該以為我唱緊餓狼傳說"},{"pid":"d1698714702b51f97d610c52fcfce9cc6aaa1d47","tid":2126522,"uid":355064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T01:41:03.000Z","msg":"餓狼傳說 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8cf7ab3732c58a2b503b498535ae57cdadd7a44","tid":2126522,"uid":48161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T01:43:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/8/80/Little_Lam_Lam.gif/revision/latest?cb=20130202151448\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2F8%2F80%2FLittle_Lam_Lam.gif%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20130202151448&h=77a4d125&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n咁樣?"},{"pid":"a55088fce014d297ddd11b5ef3281119a6f31a30","tid":2126522,"uid":203036,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b8cf7ab3732c58a2b503b498535ae57cdadd7a44","tid":2126522,"uid":48161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T01:43:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/8/80/Little_Lam_Lam.gif/revision